    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Bolloré Logistics India Holdings Services. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Distribution Manager to strengthen our Indore-based team.\n\nAbout Bolloré Logistics India Holdings Services:\nBolloré Logistics India Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bolloré Logistics India Holdings Services!",
